      "content": "data editing? that sounds terrifying. if they can just \"curate\" what stays and what goes, what's the end goal? it feels like they are trying to make it so i never even existed in certain contexts. i'm starting to wonder if this is part of something bigger, like a way to scrub people who know too much or just don't fit the narrative they want to push. do you think there are actual protocols for this kind of thing?",
